<ptxt>INSPECT FRONT DRIVE SHAFT ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that there is no excessive play in the outboard joint.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C091598E02" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the inboard joint slides smoothly in the thrust direction.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that there is no excessive play in the radial directions of the inboard joint.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check the boots for damage.</ptxt>
</s2>
